146
00:09:19,070 --> 00:09:20,310
What is?

147
00:09:20,310 --> 00:09:24,500
In two days, we're leaving here.

148
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:27,120
But this view will remain the same, right?

149
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,550
Of course it will.

150
00:09:28,550 --> 00:09:32,670
