locations we've never been...

159
00:10:01,780 --> 00:10:04,620
So many people are living 
so many kinds of lives.

160
00:10:05,420 --> 00:10:08,090
Every day, without stopping.

161
00:10:08,570 --> 00:10:09,920
That's amazing!

162
00:10:10,430 --> 00:10:12,920
Even though it's common sense.

163
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:15,630
But I know what you're getting at.

164
00:10:18,860 --> 00:10:19,960
Hinata-san?

165
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:20,510
What?

166
00:10:21,250 --> 00:10:23,140
You're hiding something, aren't you?

167
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:26,020
You're <i>hiding something</i>, aren't you?

168
00:10:44,230 --> 00:10:46,340
