169
00:10:46,340 --> 00:10:50,430
Well... I'm sure it'll turn up.

170
00:10:50,430 --> 00:10:51,670
It's so important, after all.

171
00:10:52,130 --> 00:10:55,870
But then it would have come up 
after all this searching, right?

172
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:57,670
That's true...

173
